ReallyMe OpenID4VP implements OpenID for Verifiable Presentations protocol
infrastructure and depends on ReallyMe cryptographic and identity components
for primitive cryptography, JOSE handling, credential envelope formats, and
profile-specific credential support. Dependency license terms are recorded in
the package manifests and enforced by the repository dependency policy.

